800
00:49:32.748 --> 00:49:33.989
<i>...well. it doesn't last long.</i>

801
00:49:34.058 --> 00:49:35.713
[pounding on door]

802
00:49:35.748 --> 00:49:36.886
[man]
Police!

803
00:49:36.955 --> 00:49:38.851
<i>¡Policía!</i>

804
00:49:38.886 --> 00:49:40.231
Shit.

805
00:49:40.334 --> 00:49:43.231
- ♪ tense music
- [pounding on door]

806
00:49:45.058 --> 00:49:46.748
[snapping fingers]

807
00:49:46.851 --> 00:49:49.610
[man] Open that fucking door.
Chet Davis!

808
00:49:52.989 --> 00:49:54.196
[sighs]

809
00:49:54.265 --> 00:49:56.024
You scared the shit
out of me. brother.

810
00:49:56.093 --> 00:49:58.300
I'm back in the saddle.

811
00:49:59.506 --> 00:50:00.713
Ma'am.

812
00:50:01.748 --> 00:50:04.196
♪ ominous music

813
00:50:04.231 --> 00:50:06.093
- You gonna invite me in?
- Yeah. come in.

814
00:50:07.886 --> 00:50:09.920
Well. this is delightful.

815
00:50:10.748 --> 00:50:12.265
[crickets chirping]

816
00:50:14.817 --> 00:50:16.437
[vehicle approaching]

817
00:50:31.231 --> 00:50:32.644
[engine turns off]

818
00:50:40.748 --> 00:50:42.196
What you up to. honey?

819
00:50:47.196 --> 00:50:48.368
The plan.

820
00:50:48.437 --> 00:50:49.955
Mm.

821
00:50:50.024 --> 00:50:53.196
If we can't afford the life
that we want right now...

822
00:50:53.265 --> 00:50:54.472
Mm-hmm?

823
00:50:56.231 --> 00:50:58.610
...we'll make it work together.

824
00:51:01.024 --> 00:51:02.989
You give me a week.

825
00:51:03.024 --> 00:51:06.541
I'll know everything there is
to know about Beulah Jackson.

826
00:51:07.300 --> 00:51:09.748
Well. let me tell you
about Beulah Jackson.

827
00:51:11.231 --> 00:51:13.058
About three weeks ago.

828
00:51:13.127 --> 00:51:15.644
I found a dead body
on our property.

829
00:51:16.506 --> 00:51:19.334
It floated over
from the 10-Petal.

830
00:51:20.782 --> 00:51:22.300
I took care of it.

831
00:51:23.472 --> 00:51:25.989
But we need
to be careful with this family.

832
00:51:26.058 --> 00:51:28.300
♪ quiet. dramatic music ♪

833
00:51:28.403 --> 00:51:30.300
Why didn't you tell me?

834
00:51:33.817 --> 00:51:36.265
[sighs] Peace. I guess.

835
00:51:38.437 --> 00:51:40.300
Well. peace will have to wait.

836
00:51:42.403 --> 00:51:46.644
♪
